COSMIC KATY. 
It’s not you, it’s your star sign.  
- Soft stretch fabric. 
- High neck. 
- Large vegan leather collar. 
- Adjustable vegan leather straps. 
 - Mesh underlay. 
 - Sleeve details. 
 - Skater skirt. 
- Fitted. 
 Be a celestial beauty in our ‘Cosmic Katy’ Suspender dress. Conjured in soft, stretch fabric with stretch mesh underlay to create the perfect fit. Complete with a skater skirt bottom, adjustable faux leather straps and faux leather collar you’ll feel outta this world. A staple piece for any star gazer.

movies.title: The Crow
movies.cast: Brandon Lee, Michael Wincott, Rochelle Davis
movies.summary: A man brutally murdered comes back to life as an undead avenger of his and his fiancée's murder.

movies.title: Interview with the Vampire: The Vampire Chronicles
movies.cast: Brad Pitt, Tom Cruise, Antonio Banderas
movies.summary: A vampire tells his epic life story: love, betrayal, loneliness, and hunger

movies.title: The Rocky Horror Picture Show
movies.cast: Tim Curry, Susan Sarandon, Barry Bostwick
movies.summary: A newly-engaged couple have a breakdown in an isolated area and must seek shelter at the bizarre residence of Dr. Frank-n-Furter.

movies.title: Edward Scissorhands
movies.cast: Johnny Depp, Winona Ryder, Dianne Wiest
movies.summary: An artificial man, who was incompletely constructed and has scissors for hands, leads a solitary life. Then one day, a suburban lady meets him and introduces him to her world.

movies.title: Labyrinth
movies.cast: David Bowie, Jennifer Connelly, Toby Froud
movies.summary: Sixteen-year-old Sarah is given thirteen hours to solve a labyrinth and rescue her baby brother Toby when her wish for him to be taken away is granted by the Goblin King Jareth.

movies.title: Beetlejuice
movies.cast: Alec Baldwin, Geena Davis, Michael Keaton
movies.summary: The spirits of a deceased couple are harassed by an unbearable family that has moved into their home, and hire a malicious spirit to drive them out

movies.title: The Addams Family
movies.cast: Anjelica Huston, Raul Julia, Christopher Lloyd
movies.summary: Con artists plan to fleece an eccentric family using an accomplice who claims to be their long-lost uncle.

movies.title: Dark City
movies.cast: Rufus Sewell, Kiefer Sutherland, Jennifer Connelly
movies.summary: A man struggles with memories of his past, which include a wife he cannot remember and a nightmarish world no one else ever seems to wake up from.

movies.title: The Phantom of the Opera
movies.cast: Gerard Butler, Emmy Rossum, Patrick Wilson
movies.summary: A young soprano becomes the obsession of a disfigured and murderous musical genius who lives beneath the Paris Opéra House.

movies.title: Sleepy Hollow
movies.cast: Johnny Depp, Christina Ricci, Miranda Richardson
movies.summary: Ichabod Crane is sent to Sleepy Hollow to investigate the decapitations of three people, with the culprit being the legendary apparition, The Headless Horseman

movies.title: Ginger Snaps
movies.cast: Emily Perkins, Katharine Isabelle, Kris Lemche
movies.summary: Two death-obsessed sisters, outcasts in their suburban neighborhood, must deal with the tragic consequences when one of them is bitten by a deadly werewolf

movies.title: Constantine
movies.cast: Keanu Reeves, Rachel Weisz, Djimon Hounsou
movies.summary: Supernatural exorcist and demonologist John Constantine helps a policewoman prove her sister's death was not a suicide, but something more

movies.title: The Nightmare Before Christmas
movies.cast: Danny Elfman (voice), Chris Sarandon (voice), Catherine O'Hara (voice)
movies.summary: Jack Skellington, king of Halloween Town, discovers Christmas Town, but his attempts to bring Christmas to his home causes confusion.

movies.title: Coraline
movies.cast: Dakota Fanning(voice), Teri Hatcher(voice), John Hodgman(voice)
movies.summary: An adventurous 11-year-old girl finds another world that is a strangely idealized version of her frustrating home, but it has sinister secrets.

movies.title: Corpse Bride
movies.genre: Animation, Drama, Family, Fantasy, Musical, Romance
movies.cast: Johnny Depp(voice), Helena Bonham Carter(voice), Emily Watson(voice)
movies.summary: When a shy groom practices his wedding vows in the inadvertent presence of a deceased young woman, she rises from the grave assuming he has married her.

movies.title: The Craft
movies.cast: Robin Tunney, Fairuza Balk, Neve Campbell
movies.summary: A newcomer to a Catholic prep high school falls in with a trio of outcast teenage girls who practice witchcraft, and they all soon conjure up various spells and curses against those who anger them.
